{{2019冠狀病毒病疫情邊欄}}
在[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]期间，[[南极洲|南极洲]]至2020年12月出現首例病例。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|author=Taylor|first=Adam|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2020/03/24/one-continent-remains-untouched-by-coronavirus-antarctica/|title=One continent remains untouched by the coronavirus: Antarctica|date=2020-03-24|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=2020-04-03|author2=Pitrelli|first2=Stefano|archivedate=2020-04-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401225655/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2020/03/24/one-continent-remains-untouched-by-coronavirus-antarctica/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Torres|first=Elle|url=https://abcnews.go.com/International/life-antarctica-continent-case-coronavirus/story?id=69716325|title=What life is like on Antarctica, the only continent without a case of coronavirus|date=2020-03-20|work=ABC News|accessdate=2020-04-03|archivedate=2020-04-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401135314/https://abcnews.go.com/International/life-antarctica-continent-case-coronavirus/story?id=69716325|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Agence France-Presse|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/australasia/article/3077724/pacific-islands-antarctic-bases-coronavirus-free-living-some|title=Pacific islands, Antarctic bases: coronavirus-free living in some of Earth's most isolated places|date=2020-03-31|work=South China Morning Post|accessdate=2020-04-03|archivedate=2020-04-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403015046/https://www.scmp.com/news/asia/australasia/article/3077724/pacific-islands-antarctic-bases-coronavirus-free-living-some|dead-url=no}}</ref>至此[[地球|地球]]上所有[[洲|大洲]]及[[洲#地质学|大陆]]上均出现有关COVID-19的病例报告。

== 背景 ==
2020年1月12日，[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]（WHO）查明造成[[中华人民共和国|中国]][[湖北省|湖北省]][[武汉市|武汉市]]人群的病因。相关呼吸系统疾病的信息已于2019年12月31日报告，WHO证实是一种新型[[冠状病毒|冠状病毒]]。<ref name="Elsevier">{{Cite web|title=Novel Coronavirus Information Center|url=https://www.elsevier.com/connect/coronavirus-information-center|accessdate=2020-03-15|author=Elsevier|date=|work=Elsevier Connect|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200130171622/https://www.elsevier.com/connect/coronavirus-information-center|archivedate=2020-01-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Reynolds4March2020">{{Cite news|author=Reynolds|first=Matt|url=https://www.wired.co.uk/article/china-coronavirus|title=What is coronavirus and how close is it to becoming a pandemic?|date=2020-03-04|work=Wired UK|accessdate=2020-03-05|issn=1357-0978|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305104806/https://www.wired.co.uk/article/china-coronavirus|archivedate=2020-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2019冠状病毒病的[[病死率|病死率]]低于2003年的[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症|SARS]]<ref name="Imperial13March2020">{{Cite web|title=Crunching the numbers for coronavirus|url=https://www.imperial.ac.uk/news/196137/crunching-numbers-coronavirus/|accessdate=2020-03-15|work=Imperial News|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319084913/https://www.imperial.ac.uk/news/196137/crunching-numbers-coronavirus/|archivedate=2020-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Gov.ukHCIDDef">{{Cite web|title=High consequence infectious diseases (HCID); Guidance and information about high consequence infectious diseases and their management in England|url=https://www.gov.uk/guidance/high-consequence-infectious-diseases-hcid|accessdate=2020-03-17|work=GOV.UK|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303051938/https://www.gov.uk/guidance/high-consequence-infectious-diseases-hcid|archivedate=2020-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但[[传播途径|传播率]]却更高，死亡人数众多。<ref name="WFSA">{{Cite web|title=World Federation Of Societies of Anaesthesiologists – Coronavirus|url=https://www.wfsahq.org/resources/coronavirus|accessdate=2020-03-15|work=www.wfsahq.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200312233527/https://www.wfsahq.org/resources/coronavirus|archivedate=2020-03-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 出现确诊病例前 ==
{{2019冠狀病毒病病例數/南極洲圖表|barwidth=thin}}
来到南极科考站的人们必须进行[[隔離_(醫療)|隔离]]和[[2019冠状病毒病|COVID-19]]筛查。<ref name=":0"></ref>澳大利亚和德国的南极科考站配备有[[口罩|口罩]]。尚不确定美国和英国科考站是否配备有口罩。英国南极调查局针对疫情采取了预防措施。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bas.ac.uk/media-post/british-antarctic-survey-response-to-covid-19/|title=British Antarctic Survey response to COVID-19|date=2020-03-24|work=British Antarctic Survey|accessdate=2020-04-03|archivedate=2020-04-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402232258/https://www.bas.ac.uk/media-post/british-antarctic-survey-response-to-covid-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

由于疫情对旅行造成的影响，英国调查人员从南极洲撤离时遇到了麻烦。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-52187620|title=Coronavirus complicates journeys home from Antarctica|work=BBC News|author=Amos|first=Jonathan|date=2020-04-07|accessdate=2020-04-20|archivedate=2020-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418191339/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-52187620|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2020年4月，[[2019冠狀病毒病國際郵輪疫情|一艘前往南极洲的游轮]]中有近60％的乘客COVID-19检测结果呈阳性。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/07/americas/greg-mortimer-cruise-ship-coronavirus-intl-hnk/index.html|title=Passengers to be evacuated from Antarctic cruise ship after almost 60% test positive for coronavirus|work=CNN|author=Griffiths|first=James|author2=Castillo|first2=Jackie|date=2020-04-08|accessdate=2020-04-20|archivedate=2020-04-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417091510/https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/07/americas/greg-mortimer-cruise-ship-coronavirus-intl-hnk/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/antarctic-cruise-ship-coronavirus-outbreak-2020-4|title=Nearly 60% of the passengers on an Antarctic cruise ship have tested positive for the coronavirus|work=Business Insider|author=Al-Arshani|first=Sarah|date=2020-04-09|accessdate=2020-04-20|archivedate=2020-04-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418191500/https://www.businessinsider.com/antarctic-cruise-ship-coronavirus-outbreak-2020-4|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

{{As of|2020|April|14}}，南极洲的基地只剩下维持基本运转的最少人员，访客则受到限制，科学研究也受到影响。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-antarctica-feature/isolated-within-isolation-keeping-out-coronavirus-in-the-frozen-antarctic-idUSKCN21W2O4|title='Isolated within isolation': keeping out coronavirus in the frozen Antarctic|work=Reuters|author=Laing|first=Aislinn|author2=Garrison|first2=Cassandra|date=2020-04-14|accessdate=2020-04-20|archivedate=2020-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420055106/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-antarctica-feature/isolated-within-isolation-keeping-out-coronavirus-in-the-frozen-antarctic-idUSKCN21W2O4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

由于疫情，原定于2020年中期举办的有关南极洲的几场会议被取消。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.antarctica.gov.au/news/2020/international-antarctic-conferences-cancelled-due-to-coronavirus|title=International Antarctic conferences cancelled due to coronavirus|date=2020-03-19|work=Australian Antarctic Division|accessdate=2020-04-03|archivedate=2020-03-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323025048/http://www.antarctica.gov.au/news/2020/international-antarctic-conferences-cancelled-due-to-coronavirus|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 确诊情况 ==

2020年12月，[[智利|智利]]的[[智利南极领地|南极基地]][[贝纳尔多·奥希金斯将军站|贝纳尔多·奥希金斯将军站]]爆发疫情，36人感染SARS-CoV-2<ref>{{Cite web |title=南極洲防疫失守 至少36人染疫 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202012230378.aspx |accessdate=2020-12-23 |author=羅楚瑜 |date=2020-12-22 |publisher=中央通訊社 |language=zh-hant |editor=張佑之 |location=聖地牙哥 |archive-date=2021-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102010612/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202012230378.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC">{{Cite web |title=新冠疫情：南極洲首次發現感染病例 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-55421129 |accessdate=2020-12-23 |date=2020-12-23 |publisher=BBC News 中文 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2021-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102051837/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-55421129 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=[新闻30分]智利一南极基地出现新冠肺炎疫情 36人新冠病毒检测结果呈阳性 |url=https://tv.cctv.com/2020/12/23/VIDEaNQov9rQmu9E4PNp4hbz201223.shtml?spm=C53156045404.PGb9gs0ehsXB.0.0 |accessdate=2021-01-03 |work=tv.cctv.com |archive-date=2021-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410151153/https://tv.cctv.com/2020/12/23/VIDEaNQov9rQmu9E4PNp4hbz201223.shtml?spm=C53156045404.PGb9gs0ehsXB.0.0 }}</ref>，並在隨後幾天內增加至58人<ref name="ABC"/>。

